summary: Retexture of the elder dragon to look like a rathalos and retexture of the ancient dragon to have stripes...
descriptionHtml:
So just a retexture for monster hunter fans :)
Place the textures file here in Steam\\steamapps\\common\\skyrim\\Data

To spawn the dragons press  \"`\" or \"~\" to open the console 

To spawn Rathalos type  \"Player.placeatme F8102\"
To spawn ancient type \"Player.placeatme F811D\"
author: DigitalLion
